+### Task 10: Browser Page Layout
+
+**Files:**
+- Create: `frontend/src/pages/BrowserPage.tsx`
+- Create: `frontend/src/components/Sidebar.tsx`
+- Create: `frontend/src/components/Breadcrumb.tsx`
